<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFE66A59F72894DC1779B994" authorityName="Chasen" authorityYear="1940" box="[2260,2425,645,678]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Tylonycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="29" pageNumber="787" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="malayana">7. malayana</taxonomicName>
is currently uncertain. Monotypic.
</subSubSection>
</paragraph>
